require "fern_any_auth"

any_auth = SeedAnyAuthClient::Client.new(
  base_url: "https://api.example.com",
  token: "YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN",
  api_key: "YOUR_API_KEY"
)
any_auth.auth.get_token(
  client_id: "client_id",
  client_secret: "client_secret",
  scope: "scope"
)
